    <!-- intro section -->
    <section class="services-intro">
        <h2 class="about-detail-title sect-title intro-title">
            Aside from “how do I pronounce your name?", the second most-asked question I get is
        </h2>
        <h3 class="services-intro-subtitle rob-font">
            "What actually is transformational coaching?"
        </h3>
        <div class="intro-text">
            <p class="normal-text">
                Transformational Coaching is an inside-out approach. Essentially, it’s digging deep (not moonlight meditation deep - but if that’s your thing, you go girl) to help you make the profound changes leading to a more fulfilled, happy life. Unlike traditional life coaching, which centres around goals and surface level shifts, we take it a step further by finding and harnessing your innate power and resilience (whether you believe it’s there or not). By unearthing these qualities, together we can unlock blockers to step beyond the psychology holding you back from living a life you love. Ready to make life-changing moves? You’ve come to the right place. 
            </p>
        </div>
        
    </section>
